[[File:ExecutorXWA3.png|thumb|right|260px|The ''Cruuz'' engages the ''Executor'' in the Vergesso Asteroids]]
'''''Cruuz''''' was an [[EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate/Legends|EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate]] that saw service with the the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] [[Alliance Fleet/Legends|Fleet]] during the height of the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. The warship was destroyed by [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] forces at the [[Battle of the Bajic Shipyards]].

==Behind the scenes==
It is possible to save the ''Cruuz'' in the game, but the player must engage in combat with the Imperial warships in order to do so.

